    related_texts: ['Trimsika', 'Upanishads'],
    related_concepts: ['Vijnanavada', 'Dharma'],
    sit_with_this: "If the reality of your self and the world is fundamentally characterized by Vijnanavada, how does that shift the weight of the moral choices you make today?"
