    related_texts: ['Anubhashya', 'Upanishads'],
    related_concepts: ['Shuddhadvaita', 'Dharma'],
    sit_with_this: "If the reality of your self and the world is fundamentally characterized by Shuddhadvaita, how does that shift the weight of the moral choices you make today?"
