    related_texts: ['The Gay Science', 'Meditations'],
    related_concepts: ['Amor Fati', 'Reason'],
    sit_with_this: "If the reality of your self and the world is fundamentally characterized by Amor Fati, how does that shift the weight of the moral choices you make today?"
