    in_dialogue_with: "This concept enters into an active, fruitful dialogue with cognitive dissonance and identity politics. While cognitive dissonance and identity politics often seeks to analyze truth through a specific, structured lens, Bad Faith expands this view by highlighting the relational, intuitive, or contextual dimensions of understanding. This comparison reveals that different traditions often converge on the same fundamental problems of existence, using different vocabularies to express a shared human search for meaning.",
