    related_texts: ['Is Justified True Belief Knowledge?', 'Meditations'],
    related_concepts: ['Gettier Problem', 'Reason'],
    sit_with_this: "If the reality of your self and the world is fundamentally characterized by Gettier Problem, how does that shift the weight of the moral choices you make today?"
