    related_texts: ['Climate and Culture', 'Analects'],
    related_concepts: ['Fūdoki', 'Dao'],
    sit_with_this: "If the reality of your self and the world is fundamentally characterized by Fūdoki, how does that shift the weight of the moral choices you make today?"
