    related_texts: ['Bantu Philosophy', 'Ubuntu Oral Teachings'],
    related_concepts: ['Vital Force', 'Communalism'],
    sit_with_this: "If the reality of your self and the world is fundamentally characterized by Vital Force, how does that shift the weight of the moral choices you make today?"
